snippet.title: ForeVR Suck It Trailer
snippet.description:
https://forevr.wtf/suckit
Supported Platforms: Quest 2, Steam VR
Developer: Forevr Games Inc
Website: http://forevrgames.com/

Grab that vacuum, suck...suck..SUCK! Suck up items to grow bigger and BIGGER! Grab stars to power up, battle others in this multiplayer party game!

Game on!
